  <h2>Heirloom</h2>
  <br />
  <p>A fun, fresh and economic take on chocolate branding. Originally designing within pure CMYK constraints to aid the cost-efficiency and print-efficiency of the paper choccy milk labels, magenta, blue and black went on to colour code the different types of organic chocolate used in the Heirloom family. With matching patterns. 
